28 static std::string computeDataLayout(bool is64Bit) {
29  std::string Ret = "e";
30 
31  if (!is64Bit)
32  Ret += "-p:32:32";
33 
34  Ret += "-i64:64-v16:16-v32:32-n16:32:64";
35 
36  return Ret;
37 }

39 NVPTXSubtarget &NVPTXSubtarget::initializeSubtargetDependencies(StringRef CPU,
40  StringRef FS) {
41  // Provide the default CPU if we don't have one.
42  if (CPU.empty() && FS.size())
43  llvm_unreachable("we are not using FeatureStr");
44  TargetName = CPU.empty() ? "sm_20" : CPU;
45 
46  ParseSubtargetFeatures(TargetName, FS);
47 
48  // Set default to PTX 3.2 (CUDA 5.5)
49  if (PTXVersion == 0) {
50  PTXVersion = 32;
51  }
52 
53  return *this;
54 }
